{"tid":2239900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［放負］入嚟放底你屋企人有幾廢","createTime":"2020-10-12T10:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T11:11:12.000Z","uid":113371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b738c27854a46357ba9f61c4487a7bfa98302824","tid":2239900,"uid":113371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"屋企人有養大我，但越大個就發覺屋企人有幾廢。<br />\n<br />\n老母：賭錢賭到由我大學開錢問我攞錢。<br />\n家姐：成家立室，但成日咩都要人幫，又鍾意好高騖遠，成日話投資呢樣投資嗰樣，話唔資助佢就當借，但從來無還過。近排疫情，幾個月前又借咗啲，但唔知幾時還。<br />\n<br />\n有時真係覺得屋企人好煩，點解出嚟社會咁耐仲要個細佬幫，真係有夠攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4130bd5495116872558124c06e6a0965c3bc9f70","tid":2239900,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b80e156ec664ee51d885e094917aa5f6143b074","tid":2239900,"uid":42414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"點解佢地咁廢都可以因為身邊寵壞而成"},{"pid":"51a7ae38cce96bba3f6162fc710d5a102a7270a5","tid":2239900,"uid":327049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4fad9ee5d4ebc17e703b05f47164b099949642","tid":2239900,"uid":327049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a7ae38cce96bba3f6162fc710d5a102a7270a5","tid":2239900,"uid":327049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:17:34.000Z","msg":"細細個我*成日食公仔麵"},{"pid":"49fa063c1ecbbf10660176d97a13ad649c181f71","tid":2239900,"uid":113371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"有啲廢屋企人真心煩同難頂"}]}